<CONTENT id="_800710_1"><TITLE value="Topic 1.6 AI Risks"/><TITLECOLOR value="#000000"/><DESCRIPTION
   value=""/><BODY><TEXT>&lt;div data-layout-row="b8830600-2413-4658-b01e-6c671eec21b8"&gt;&lt;div data-layout-column="1de0c8e3-65b0-42c8-95e0-f46efd085d62" data-layout-column-width="12"&gt;&lt;div data-bbid="bbml-editor-id_2460284e-3858-463e-a080-77cd1e5aa0f5"&gt;&lt;h4&gt;1.6 AI Risks&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;span style="color: #e72218"&gt;AI Risks&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Artificial Intelligence plays an important role in the economic, social, scientific, financial and military sectors, and because of that, we should be extremely careful as there are many risks associated with the development of AI.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Mechanical Arts are of the ambiguous use, serving as well for remedy.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Francis Bacon, The wisdom of the Ancients, 1609&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We always need to assess what we do with AI:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-1692500_1" data-bbtype="attachment" data-bbfile="{&amp;quot;alternativeText&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Scale of justice Ref: https://www.publicdomainpictures.net/en/view-image.php?image=72186&amp;amp;picture=scales-of-justice &amp;quot;,&amp;quot;linkName&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;M1_Scale.png&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;mimeType&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;image/png&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;render&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;inline&amp;quot;}"&gt;M1_Scale.png&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: left;"&gt;As we develop AI applications we will incur risks of misuse, the figure below lists some of the key areas that are already apparent:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;a href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-1692601_1" data-bbtype="attachment" data-bbfile="{&amp;quot;alternativeText&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;AI Risks versus benefits&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;linkName&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;M1_risk_versus_benifit.png&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;mimeType&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;image/png&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;render&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;inline&amp;quot;}"&gt;M1_risk_versus_benifit.png&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Biased decision making&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Careless misuse of &lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;machine learning algorithms&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt; may results in decisions that are biased by race, gender, etc. For example:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Loan applications&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Employment&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Evaluating payroll&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Credit card applications&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;pre&gt;Suggested reading&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;For more information, read this article that speaks about gender bias.&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Surveillance &amp;amp; persuasion&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;AI speech recognition, computer vision and natural language understanding can be used in scalable fashion to perform mass surveillance of individuals and detect activities of interest.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;By tailoring &lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;information flows&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;to individuals through social media based on &lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;machine learning techniques&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;, political behaviour can be modified and controlled to a certain extent.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre&gt;Suggested reading&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;For more information, read this article on "Cambridge Analytica".&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Lethal Autonomous Weapons&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Lethal Autonomous Weapons are defined by the United Nations as:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Weapons that can locate, select, and eliminate human targets without human interventions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The primary concern is &lt;strong&gt;Scalability&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The technologies required for these weapons are similar to the technologies used in &lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;autonomous driving&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Impact on employment&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Robotics, powered by AI, has raised a valid concern about &lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;machines eliminating jobs&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;. This topic is becoming a major focus of governments around the world.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Safety critical applications&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;As AI techniques advance, they are increasingly being used in &lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;high stake and safety critical applications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;such as the medical field and the autonomous driving.&amp;nbsp;Many conversations are happening around the globe about the decision making processes as &lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;people lives are at stake&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre&gt;Suggested reading&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;Check out this article on an actual fatality due to self driving cars.&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Cyber security&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;AI techniques are useful in defending against cyber attacks by detecting unusual patterns of behavior, but will also contribute to the potency (influence), &lt;em&gt;survivability&lt;/em&gt; (capable of withstanding attack) and proliferation of &lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;malware&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h5&gt;References&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Artificial intelligence a modern approach&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;by Stuart J. Russell and Peter Norvig, Chapter 1&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.openglobalrights.org/addressing-gender-bias-in-artificial-intelligence-and-automation/"&gt;https://www.openglobalrights.org/addressing-gender-bias-in-artificial-intelligence-and-automation/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.wired.com/story/cambridge-analytica-facebook-privacy-awakening/"&gt;https://www.wired.com/story/cambridge-analytica-facebook-privacy-awakening/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2018/3/19/17139518/uber-self-driving-car-fatal-crash-tempe-arizona"&gt;https://www.theverge.com/2018/3/19/17139518/uber-self-driving-car-fatal-crash-tempe-arizona&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</TEXT><TYPE
